# Design system conventions

- Tokens: `src/app/globals.css` (`--c-*`) + `tailwind.config.ts`. Light theme only.
- Primitives: `src/components/ui.tsx`. Brand: `src/components/brand/Brand.tsx`.
- Rail: pinned header (workspace → search) and footer (hire + profile); middle uses `.rail-scroll`.
- Side panes: `ResizablePane` — content flush to the seam; handles overlay; main work view is never collapsible.
- Narrow panes: `min-w-0` + `truncate` on flex text. Prefer existing AdeHQ patterns over new visual languages.
